folder. Right click on the game in yuzu&amp;nbsp; and click on mod data location.&#13;
 Yuzu"s mod folder is:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;yuzu\load\0100F2C0115B6000&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Make sure the folder structure follows&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Yoink! ultra hand mod\romfs\Sound\Resource\Stream&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Make sure Pack_SpecialPower.bars.zs file is in the Resource folder and UltraHand_Shot_00.bwav file is in the Stream folder.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Legal stuff:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Halo Reach © Microsoft Corporation. Yoink! Halo Ultra Hand mod was created under Microsoft's "Game Content Usage Rules" using &#13;
