uilt and test on Switch and Yuzu 1.2.1&lt;br&gt;Please use Tkmm for other versions &lt;br&gt;Include tkcl info file for easy merging&lt;br&gt;Mod requires higher priority &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor SelectedElement"&gt;Thanks TotK/BotW community for help/teaching&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Special Thanks to everyone developing tools &lt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Thanks Nintendo for making this all possible&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;First version &lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;- attack up effect&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Second version&lt;/span&gt; &lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Head&lt;/span&gt; (QuietnessUp)&lt;br&gt;- QuietnessUp&lt;br&gt;- ClimbSpeedUp&lt;br&gt;- DivingMobilityUp&lt;br&gt;- ResistElectric&lt;br&gt;- AttackUpThunderstorm&lt;br&gt;- ChargePowerUpThunderstorm&lt;br&gt;- ResitLightning&lt;br&gt;- DecreaseSwimStamina&lt;br&gt;- ClimbWaterfall&lt;br&gt;- NoSlip&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Upper&lt;/span&gt; (ResistCold)&lt;br&gt;- AttackUp&lt;br&gt;- DefenseUp&lt;br&gt;- ResistCold&lt;br&gt;- AttackUpCold&lt;br&gt;- MiasmaGuard&lt;br&gt;- ChargeSpeedUp&lt;br&gt;- DecreaseChargeAttackStamina&lt;br&gt;- AttackUpBone&lt;br&gt;- LightFootprints&lt;br&gt;- ChargePowerUpCold&lt;br&gt;- ResistFreeze&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;lower&lt;/span&gt; (ResistHot)&lt;br&gt;- AllSpeed&lt;br&gt;- ResistHot&lt;br&gt;- AttackUpHot&lt;br&gt;- SwimSpeedUp&lt;br&gt;- ExStaminaMaxUp&lt;br&gt;- ChargePowerUpHot&lt;br&gt;- NoBurning&lt;br&gt;- SandMoveUp&lt;br&gt;- SnowMoveUp&lt;br&gt;- NightMoveSpeedUp&lt;br&gt;</description>
