ve corresponding elemental effects&lt;br&gt;Added dragon parts to Blupee Rabbit drop table&lt;br&gt;All weapons have increased durability&lt;br&gt;This mod should have high priority &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Tkmm info&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; file&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt; included&lt;/span&gt; for easy merging &lt;br&gt;Created and tested for Switch and Yuzu on 1.2.1 &lt;br&gt;For other version please use &lt;a href="https://tkmm.org/" target="_blank"&gt;Tkmm&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;Check out TotK &lt;a href="https://discord.gg/yJrtEV8W" target="_blank"&gt;Discord&lt;/a&gt; for any help &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Thanks &lt;a href="https://sketchfab.com/3d-models/ice-sword-931fed1aeedc4d6baf39a58b120c7e95" target="_blank"&gt;Sketchfab&lt;/a&gt; for the additional weapon &lt;a href="https://sketchfab.com/3d-models/autumn-sword-28c2c7262e334e529709fb88e019a716" target="_blank"&gt;models&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;br&gt;I'll also include them in a large weapon pack very soon. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor SelectedElement"&gt;Thanks everyone at TotK/BotW community for help/teaching.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Special Thanks to everyone developing tools &lt;3.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Thanks to Nintendo for making this all possible.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
